<HEAD>Newspaper Industry Technology Exposition Opens</HEAD>
<DATELINE>NEW ORLEANS (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Printing presses, newsroom computers and other
equipment filled two New Orleans convention centers at the opening
of the American Newspaper Publishers Association technology
exposition.
   More than 300 exhibitors spread out over 320,000 square feet to
show off the latest equipment for the big business of newspapering.
